43
00:02:13,900 --> 00:02:14,820
The scene is still there.

44
00:02:15,060 --> 00:02:16,420
You can go and see for yourselves.

45
00:02:16,980 --> 00:02:18,540
Miss Wang, you have a sharp tongue.

46
00:02:18,700 --> 00:02:20,340
Do you really think I'd risk my own life

47
00:02:20,460 --> 00:02:21,940
just to frame you?

48
00:02:22,540 --> 00:02:23,820
I have a sharp tongue?

49
00:02:24,140 --> 00:02:26,220
Liu Rumeng, I'll tear your mouth shut!

50
00:02:31,340 --> 00:02:31,980
Rumeng!

51
