64
00:02:57,700 --> 00:03:00,220
Listen. If anything happens to Rumeng,

65
00:03:01,060 --> 00:03:03,220
I will never forgive you!

66
00:03:20,580 --> 00:03:21,540
What happened today...

67
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:24,140
I'll settle the score with you later.

68
00:03:26,700 --> 00:03:28,380
She was probably the one
who poisoned her.

69
00:03:28,380 --> 00:03:29,020
Exactly.

70
00:03:31,540 --> 00:03:32,500
Miss Wang.

71
