81
00:05:44,420 --> 00:05:45,860
Miss Wang, are you alright?

82
00:05:48,620 --> 00:05:49,340
Get out!

83
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:58,740
Liu Rumeng,

84
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:02,820
the kidnapping wasn't my doing.

85
00:06:04,380 --> 00:06:06,100
Then there's only one possibility.

86
00:06:08,820 --> 00:06:11,140
You staged all of this yourself.

87
00:06:13,140 --> 00:06:14,740
How do you know so much?

88
00:06:15,380 --> 00:06:16,180
Are you Qingmao?

89
00:06:18,540 --> 00:06:19,620
Are you Lin Qingyi?

90
00:06:24,660 --> 00:06:26,620
Rumeng, are you alright now?

91
00:06:30,780 --> 00:06:31,940
I've made arrangements
with the authorities.

92
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:32,700
They will inspect

93
00:06:32,700 --> 00:06:34,300
Wang Penghui's dock tonight.

94
00:06:35,260 --> 00:06:36,740
He'll likely be working frantically
tonight.

95
00:06:39,260 --> 00:06:40,180
The thing you're looking for...

96
00:06:40,500 --> 00:06:41,940
Are you sure it's in the study?

97
00:06:43,540 --> 00:06:44,980
